<paragraph id="4271715DF2209CC5CCB2C284BC08D82F" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Brazil, 
<normalizedToken id="E97054A01463DAB9F4C6F7DCDC3DABA9" originalValue="Perú">Peru</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D91394A2B9186E12AE523D78FEC1EB6A" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" type="notes">
<paragraph id="FEA94EE00C4DD935BBFEAFBD697E26EA" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C9A6BEEF7C048B44A8930BBD2477F3CD" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Currently, three described species are assigned to this genus: however, eight species are represented in the NMNH collection. A taxonomic revision of the group is needed.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
